###### CREATE FLOW

before_validation
→ validate
→ after_validation
→ before_save
→ before_create
-> before_commit
→ INSERT
→ after_create
→ after_save
→ after_commit


#### UPDATE FLOW

before_validation
→ validate
→ after_validation
→ before_save
→ before_update
→ UPDATE
→ after_update
→ after_save
→ after_commit


### DELETE 

before_destroy
→ DELETE
→ after_destroy
→ after_commit (on: :destroy)


################

BEGIN TRANSACTION
│
├── before_validation
├── validate
├── after_validation
├── before_save
├── before_create
├── INSERT
├── after_create
├── after_save
│
COMMIT
│
└── after_commit   ✅ (outside transaction)


###

BEGIN TRANSACTION
│
├── before_save
├── before_create
├── INSERT ❌ fails
│
ROLLBACK
│
└── after_rollback   ✅

